sentences.sContent: The user name should consist of alphanumeric characters and be a valid structure for all systems within an organization so that each person only has one user name.
sentences.sContent_eng: The user name should consist of alphanumeric characters and be a valid structure for all systems within an organization so that each person only has one user name.
sentences.sCn: 用户名应该由字母数字字符组成，并且对于组织内部所有的系统都应该是有效的结构，以便每个人只使用一个用户名。
